Invocation Name: west hollywood calendar
des:
The official calendar Skill for The City of West Hollywood is the easiest way to find out what’s happening in the Creative City. Just say "Alexa, ask West Hollywood Calendar what’s happening today?” to hear about local events in West Hollywood, CA.

You can also say “Alexa, ask West Hollywood Calendar what’s happening this weekend?” or “Alexa, ask West Hollywood Calendar tomorrow?”

To hear the details of an event just say the event number.

For a full list of events, visit http://www.weho.org/city-hall/calendar
